SQL_STMT_U.val: select ACCD_DESCRIPTION, ACCD_ACCT_DATE, ACCD_ACCC_CHANGENO, ACCC_MUTAFACTORING, ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT, ACCC_MUTARETENTION, ACCC_MUTADISPUTES, ACCC_MUTASPECIAL, ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS, ACCC_MUTASTOCK, ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN, ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE, ACCC_MUTADEBTORS, ACCC_MUTARESERVE, ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT from :1/ACCD join :1/ACCC on ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = ACCD_ACCT_ADMNO and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = ACCD_ACCT_CLNTNO and ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ACCD_ACCT_DATE and ACCC_CHANGENO = ACCD_ACCC_CHANGENO and ACCC_MUTTYPE < 91 where ACCD_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and ACCD_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and ACCD_ACCT_DATE between ':4' and ':5' and ACCD_LINENO = 1 and not(exists (select * from :1/MKOD where MKOD_ACCC_MUTTYPE = ACCC_MUTTYPE)) order by ACCD_DESCRIPTION, ACCD_ACCT_DATE, ACCD_ACCC_CHANGENO for fetch only

select ACCC_ACCT_DATE, ACCC_CHANGENO, ACCC_MUTAFACTORING, ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT, ACCC_MUTARETENTION, ACCC_MUTADISPUTES, ACCC_MUTASPECIAL, ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS, ACCC_MUTASTOCK, ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN, ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE, ACCC_MUTADEBTORS, ACCC_MUTARESERVE, ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT from :1/ACCC where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and ACCC_ACCT_DATE between ':4' and ':5' and ACCC_MUTTYPE < 91 and not(exists (select * from :1/MKOD where MKOD_ACCC_MUTTYPE = ACCC_MUTTYPE)) and not(exists( select * from :1/ACCD where ACCD_ACCT_ADMNO = ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO and ACCD_ACCT_CLNTNO = ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO and ACCD_ACCT_DATE = ACCC_ACCT_DATE and ACCD_ACCC_CHANGENO = ACCC_CHANGENO)) order by ACCC_ACCT_DATE, ACCC_CHANGENO for fetch only

select cast(sum(TMKO_MUTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTASETTLEMENT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTARETENTION) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTADISPUTES) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTASPECIAL) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTAARRANGEMENTS) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTASTOCK) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTAEXTRAFIN) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTADEBTORS) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTARESERVE) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(TMKO_MUTAINVESTMENT) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/TMKO where TMKO_ADMNO = :2 and TMKO_CLNTNO = :3 for fetch only

delete from :1/TMKO A where A.TMKO_ADMNO = :2 and A.TMKO_CLNTNO = :3 and A.TMKO_NUMBERN_OWNER = 0 and not(exists(select * from :1/TMKO B where B.TMKO_ADMNO = :2 and B.TMKO_CLNTNO = :3 and B.TMKO_NUMBERN_OWNER = A.TMKO_CODE_NUMBERN))
